text: Milltownpass GAA is a Gaelic Athletic Association club located in the town of Milltownpass in County Westmeath, Ireland. ==History== The team was founded in 1977 and participates in both men's and women's leagues. ==Notable Players== ==References== ==External links== * http://www.milltownpassgaa.ie/ Category:Gaelic Athletic Association clubs in County Westmeath Category:1977 establishments in Ireland
